{
  "stem": "27509.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They had two separate organizations, two different synagogues there, because they are quite a different order of-- not order of [? service ?], but the-- the music of the service, the singing, and so on, it's quite different, quite a different world.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In fact, so much so that my first business in Shanghai I've done with a Sephardic Jew trading with him in Hebrew, because my English wasn't yet of the-- of a standard to do business.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he didn't speak Russian, or Polish, or German, and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So Hebrew was the common denominator.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I struck the first deal in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, my occupations in Shanghai were varied, very varied.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know that I'm so capable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Shanghai discovered in me things I never knew that I had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] At first, we were-- you know it was-- Shanghai the sort of place where business is everything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Human life isn't worth much, because the Chinese people used to die from hunger, and cold.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Used to collect every morning in the wintertime, the corpses lying in the streets, and in the gutters, and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The money was the ruling order and value of that society.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Chinese are the business people [INAUDIBLE] you well know all over the world.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was an opportunity and a possibility in that open city for anyone with any initiative to do something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Next to the existing Russian Jewish community, with whom we could-- we could identify in terms of language, because most of those who spoke Russian-- certainly, those who spoke only Polish also had a Slavic affinity of language.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] with our mentality now processes of thinking, we are the same.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had an immediate affinity.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We lived among them in the French concession.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
